public class NewProjectWizardPage
extends org.eclipse.ui.dialogs.WizardNewProjectCreationPage

A class that creates a new Google Data wizard page. It allows setting the new Google Data project name, select the project template and provide the dependency path. It also provides the external dependency options.

                            java.lang.String title,

                            java.util.Map<java.lang.String,FileTemplateConfig> templateConfigMap)
Creates a new Google Data Project Wizard Page.

If title is null, then it won't be displayed.

If description is null, then it won't be displayed.

If image is null, then it won't be displayed.

Parameters:
pageName - the name of this page
title - the title of this page
description - the description of this page
templateConfigMap - the Map of template configuration elements
